WEBVTT

00:09.417 --> 00:11.000
- I SPIT OUT TWO KIDS,
BLEW MY HUSBAND,

00:11.000 --> 00:13.168
AND TAKING CARE
OF THIS SHITHOLE.

00:13.168 --> 00:14.834
I STILL HAD TIME
TO WATCH SHAMELESS.

00:14.834 --> 00:16.542
WHAT'S YOUR DAMN EXCUSE?

00:16.542 --> 00:17.667
$2.

00:17.667 --> 00:18.667
DID YOU SEE THAT?

00:18.667 --> 00:19.834
THESE CHEAP MOTHERFUCKERS.

00:19.834 --> 00:20.959
- I JUST WANT EVERYBODY HERE

00:20.959 --> 00:23.042
TO KNOW I'M FUCKING GAY.

00:23.042 --> 00:24.417
- AAH!

00:24.417 --> 00:26.959
I'LL FUCKING KILL YOU!
AAH!

00:26.959 --> 00:28.250
- SO YOU REALLY
CAME OUT, HUH?

00:28.250 --> 00:29.250
- IT DOESN'T MEAN
I'M GONNA WEAR

00:29.250 --> 00:30.750
A FUCKING DRESS OR ANYTHING.

00:30.750 --> 00:32.168
WHAT THE FUCK'S
GOING ON WITH YOU?

00:32.168 --> 00:33.168
ONE MINUTE YOU'RE
LIKE SUPERMAN,

00:33.168 --> 00:34.458
RUNNING AROUND
MAKING PANCAKES,

00:34.458 --> 00:36.125
TAKING PICTURES
OF THE GODDAMN SUNRISE.

00:36.125 --> 00:37.959
AND THE NEXT THING, YOU WANT TO
CUT SOMEBODY'S THROAT.

00:37.959 --> 00:40.041
- I COULDN'T HELP BUT NOTICE
THE, UH, SCHEDULE.

00:40.041 --> 00:42.209
- I SYNCED IT
TO YOUR NEW PHONE.

00:42.209 --> 00:44.876
- THE SCHEDULE, IT'S JUST--
IT'S--IT'S NOT ME.

00:44.876 --> 00:46.250
- HOW'S THAT WORKING OUT
FOR YOU?

00:46.250 --> 00:47.667
[crash]

00:47.667 --> 00:50.042
- JUST HELP ME
GRAB SOME CANDY.

00:50.042 --> 00:51.458
MY FAMILY LIVES IN THERE.

00:51.458 --> 00:52.500
- THE SUPERMARKET?

00:52.500 --> 00:54.166
- IN THE VAN.

00:54.166 --> 00:57.292
- I'M THE LAUGHING STOCK
OF THE 7TH AND 8TH GRADE.

00:57.292 --> 00:58.458
I THOUGHT HE LIKED ME.

00:58.458 --> 00:59.917
HE ASKED ME TO THE DANCE.

00:59.917 --> 01:01.084
- I'LL TAKE YOU
TO THE DANCE.

01:01.084 --> 01:02.709
- WELL, HELLO.

01:02.709 --> 01:05.042
THOSE ADORABLE CHILDREN.

01:05.042 --> 01:06.876
ROGER AND I, WE WERE
GONNA GET MARRIED

01:06.876 --> 01:10.168
AND ADOPT THEM BEFORE
HE SHOWED HIS TRUE COLORS.

01:10.168 --> 01:12.417
ALL I NEED IS
A MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE.

01:12.417 --> 01:15.083
FRANCIS GALLAGHER,
WILL YOU MARRY ME?

01:15.083 --> 01:18.000
- IT IS MY HONOR TO
DECLARE YOU MAN AND WIFE.

01:18.000 --> 01:19.083
YOU MAY KISS THE GROOM.

01:19.083 --> 01:20.625
[applause]

01:20.625 --> 01:22.084
- HE'S IN SERIOUS CONDITION,

01:22.084 --> 01:23.084
SO THEY MOVED HIM
UP THE WAITING LIST.

01:23.084 --> 01:24.500
- WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

01:24.500 --> 01:25.625
- HE'S GETTING A LIVER.
- WHERE AM I, DEBBIE?

01:25.625 --> 01:27.125
- I'M SAMMI.

01:27.125 --> 01:28.417
- I BETTER GET THE DOCTOR.

01:28.417 --> 01:30.168
- WHERE'S MAMA GOING, LIP?

01:30.168 --> 01:31.417
- DUDE, WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?
I'M CARL.

01:31.417 --> 01:32.834
- MR. GALLAGHER IS SUFFERING

01:32.834 --> 01:34.458
FROM POSTOPERATIVE DELIRIUM.

01:34.458 --> 01:37.542
- MM, MOM, STOP.
WE'RE IN PUBLIC.

01:37.542 --> 01:38.542
WAIT TILL WE GET HOME.

01:38.542 --> 01:40.041
- I'M NOT YOUR FRIEND.

01:40.041 --> 01:41.083
I'M HERE TO MAKE SURE
YOU DON'T VIOLATE

01:41.083 --> 01:42.458
THE TERMS OF YOUR PROBATION.

01:42.458 --> 01:43.876
- FIONA NEVER CAME HOME.

01:43.876 --> 01:44.876
SHE VIOLATED PROBATION.

01:44.876 --> 01:46.000
- WHERE ARE WE GOING?

01:46.000 --> 01:47.500
- LOOKS LIKE
DECATUR CORRECTIONAL.

01:47.500 --> 01:49.041
- OFF THE BUS.
SINGLE LINE.

01:49.041 --> 01:51.168
NO TALKING, NO PUSHING.

02:01.166 --> 02:04.166
[High Strung's
The Luck You Got]

02:04.166 --> 02:08.126
♪ ♪

02:08.126 --> 02:11.500
- ♪ THINK OF ALL THE LUCK
YOU GOT ♪

02:11.500 --> 02:14.500
♪ KNOW THAT
IT'S NOT FOR NAUGHT ♪

02:14.500 --> 02:17.876
♪ YOU WERE BEAMING
ONCE BEFORE ♪

02:17.876 --> 02:21.876
♪ BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT
ANYMORE ♪

02:21.876 --> 02:25.333
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

02:25.333 --> 02:28.834
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

02:28.834 --> 02:31.168
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

02:31.168 --> 02:35.709
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF? ♪

02:35.709 --> 02:42.625
♪ ♪

02:42.625 --> 02:45.834
♪ ROUND UP THE FRIENDS
YOU GOT ♪

02:45.834 --> 02:49.126
♪ KNOW THAT
THEY'RE NOT FOR NAUGHT ♪

02:49.126 --> 02:52.250
♪ YOU WERE WILLING
ONCE BEFORE ♪

02:52.250 --> 02:56.500
♪ BUT IT'S NOT LIKE THAT
ANYMORE ♪

02:56.500 --> 02:59.792
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

02:59.792 --> 03:03.500
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

03:03.500 --> 03:05.458
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

03:05.458 --> 03:09.209
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF? ♪

03:28.584 --> 03:33.750
[monitor beeping]

03:51.083 --> 03:53.333
- OW.

04:18.834 --> 04:20.001
- DAD?

04:20.001 --> 04:21.458
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

04:21.458 --> 04:23.375
- DOES THIS THING
DISPENSE MORPHINE?

04:23.375 --> 04:24.792
- ARE YOU IN PAIN?

04:24.792 --> 04:25.917
- YES.

04:25.917 --> 04:27.126
- A LOT OF PAIN?

04:27.126 --> 04:28.959
- YES. JESUS.

04:28.959 --> 04:30.125
- DADDY.

04:30.125 --> 04:31.917
DO YOU KNOW WHO I AM?

04:31.917 --> 04:33.375
- WHAT?

04:33.375 --> 04:36.500
- WHO AM I?

04:36.500 --> 04:38.834
- SAMMI.
- [gasps]

04:38.834 --> 04:42.250
- GOOD MORNING,
MR. EARLY BIRD.

04:42.250 --> 04:44.084
- WHERE--WHERE'S MY FAMILY?

04:44.084 --> 04:46.083
- I'M RIGHT HERE, DAD.
- WE'RE HERE, HONEY.

04:46.083 --> 04:48.000
- I THINK DAD'S BACK.

04:48.000 --> 04:49.458
- WHERE THE HELL ELSE
WOULD I BE?

04:49.458 --> 04:53.250
- DO YOU KNOW WHERE YOU ARE?

04:53.250 --> 04:54.417
- A HOSPITAL?

04:54.417 --> 04:56.667
- A HOSPITAL WHERE?

04:56.667 --> 04:58.208
- CHICAGO. JESUS.
[both gasp]

04:58.208 --> 05:00.042
WHAT THE HELL IS WRONG
WITH YOU TWO IDIOTS?

05:00.042 --> 05:01.000
- I'LL GO GET THE NURSE.

05:01.000 --> 05:03.417
- OH, FRANK.

05:03.417 --> 05:05.584
IT'S YOU. YOU'RE BACK!

05:05.584 --> 05:07.126
I KNEW YOU'D BE BACK.
- OH, JESUS.

05:07.126 --> 05:09.083
- MRS. GALLAGHER, I TOLD YOU
TO STAY OFF THE BED.

05:09.083 --> 05:10.375
YOU'RE GONNA RIP OUT
HIS STAPLES.

05:10.375 --> 05:11.834
- MRS. GALLAGHER?

05:11.834 --> 05:13.667
- I DON'T THINK
HE'S CONFUSED ANYMORE.

05:13.667 --> 05:15.458
- MRS. GALLAGHER?
WE'RE MARRIED?

05:15.458 --> 05:17.208
- STILL SOUNDS PRETTY CONFUSED
TO ME.

05:17.208 --> 05:19.250
- SINCE WHEN?
- OH, HONEY.

05:19.250 --> 05:20.417
YOU'RE A HOOT.

05:20.417 --> 05:22.166
I THINK HE'S IN PAIN.

05:22.166 --> 05:23.166
- YOU IN PAIN,
MR. GALLAGHER?

05:23.166 --> 05:26.166
- YES. YES, EXCRUCIATING.

05:26.166 --> 05:27.458
[groans]

05:27.458 --> 05:28.917
WHAT DO WE GOT GOING HERE?

05:28.917 --> 05:30.625
DEMEROL? VICODIN?

05:30.625 --> 05:32.000
WHAT SAY WE TOSS IN DILAUDID,

05:32.000 --> 05:34.500
TRY TO TAKE THE EDGE
OFF OF THIS BITCH?

05:34.500 --> 05:35.959
- PAIN IS A BLESSING,
MR. GALLAGHER,

05:35.959 --> 05:38.041
PART OF THE GOOD LORD'S
HEALING PROCESS.

05:38.041 --> 05:40.458
I'MA GO GET YOUR BREAKFAST.

05:40.458 --> 05:42.333
- I'M SO GLAD
YOU'RE BACK, DAD.

05:42.333 --> 05:43.917
- WE'RE MARRIED?

05:43.917 --> 05:45.168
- ISN'T IT WONDERFUL?

05:45.168 --> 05:46.542
I'M GONNA GO CALL GARY,

05:46.542 --> 05:49.042
AND HAVE HIM
BRING THE KIDS DOWN.

05:49.042 --> 05:52.125
M-MWAH!

05:52.125 --> 05:54.000
AHH.

05:54.000 --> 05:55.834
- WHO THE HELL'S GARY?

05:55.834 --> 05:58.458
- ONE OF YOUR NEW
NATIVE AMERICAN KIDS.

05:58.458 --> 06:01.209
I THINK HE'S THE ONE WITH
THE JUSTIN BIEBER HAIRCUT.

06:01.209 --> 06:05.000
- I HAVE NATIVE AMERICAN KIDS?

06:05.000 --> 06:08.417
- FIVE.

06:10.625 --> 06:15.166
[phone ringing]

06:15.166 --> 06:18.041
[upbeat rock music]

06:18.041 --> 06:26.083
♪ ♪

06:30.834 --> 06:32.500
- IT'S FUCKING FREEZING.
WHAT'S UP WITH THE HEAT?

06:32.500 --> 06:35.083
- FIONA HAS US TURNING IT DOWN
AT NIGHT, SAVE ON GAS.

06:35.083 --> 06:36.208
- CHRIST. I CAN ALMOST
SEE MY BREATH.

06:36.208 --> 06:37.792
- YEAH, YOU WILL
BE ABLE TO SOON.

06:37.792 --> 06:39.375
GAS COMPANY'S CUTTING US OFF
ON FRIDAY.

06:39.375 --> 06:40.417
- WHAT, FIONA DIDN'T PAY IT?

06:40.417 --> 06:41.792
- SHE PAID WHAT SHE COULD.

06:41.792 --> 06:42.959
- ALL RIGHT, WELL,
I GOT SOME MONEY

06:42.959 --> 06:44.333
FROM AMANDA'S FOLKS.

06:44.333 --> 06:45.375
MAKE A LIST.
WE'LL PAY SOME BILLS, YEAH?

06:45.375 --> 06:46.500
- AMANDA'S STAYING?

06:46.500 --> 06:47.917
- WHY, YOU DON'T LIKE HER?

06:47.917 --> 06:49.168
- I LIKE HER AS LONG
AS SHE'S HELPING US

06:49.168 --> 06:51.876
PAY SOME BILLS.

06:53.709 --> 06:57.083
- YO, UP.
SCHOOL.

06:57.083 --> 06:59.208
WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO
WITH HIM?

06:59.208 --> 07:00.208
- WE COULD DROP HIM OFF
AT THE BUTCHER

07:00.208 --> 07:01.667
OVER AT THE FOOD 4 LESS,

07:01.667 --> 07:03.125
SEE IF THEY'LL CHOP HIM UP
FOR BACON.

07:03.125 --> 07:05.000
- WE HAVING BACON
FOR BREAKFAST?

07:05.000 --> 07:06.542
- NAH, WE'RE EATING CHUCKIE.

07:06.542 --> 07:08.584
- OH, COOL.

07:12.834 --> 07:14.041
- SHE'S SLEEPING
WITH YOU NOW?

07:14.041 --> 07:15.292
- YOUR GIRLFRIEND
SLEEPS WITH YOU.

07:15.292 --> 07:17.041
- YEAH, AMANDA'S 20,
NOT 12.

07:17.041 --> 07:19.000
- BONNIE'S 13.

07:19.000 --> 07:20.625
- I STILL DON'T WANT HER
SLEEPING WITH YOU.

07:20.625 --> 07:22.126
- SHE DOESN'T
WANT TO HAVE SEX,

07:22.126 --> 07:23.166
SOMETHING ABOUT
HER MOM'S OLD BOYFRIEND

07:23.166 --> 07:25.166
AND A BIKER GANG.

07:38.209 --> 07:40.083
- COFFEE?
- OH, YEAH, HERE.

07:40.083 --> 07:42.792
- THANKS.
- OUTSTANDING BILLS.

07:42.792 --> 07:45.375
- JESUS. WHAT, ELECTRIC
AND RENT ARE LATE TOO?

07:45.375 --> 07:47.417
ALL RIGHT, CAN YOU GET
TO THE CHECK-CASHING PLACE?

07:47.417 --> 07:49.168
BUY SOME MONEY ORDERS TODAY?

07:49.168 --> 07:52.250
- YEAH, ABSOLUTELY.

07:52.250 --> 07:54.542
MORE LIKE 1,900 IF YOU WANT
TO PAY EVERYTHING OFF.

07:54.542 --> 07:56.417
- ALL RIGHT.
THERE YOU GO.

07:56.417 --> 07:57.417
HIDE IT IN YOUR BOOT
OR SOMETHING, OKAY?

07:57.417 --> 07:58.667
- NOBODY'S GONNA ROLL ME.

07:58.667 --> 07:59.876
I CARRY PEPPER SPRAY
AND A SHIV.

07:59.876 --> 08:01.041
- HANDING OUT MONEY?

08:01.041 --> 08:02.125
BONNIE'S BROTHERS NEED
A FEW Z-PAKS

08:02.125 --> 08:03.667
AND A COUPLE BOTTLES OF RID.

08:03.667 --> 08:05.333
- YOU KNOW, HOW MUCH LONGER
ARE BONNIE'S

08:05.333 --> 08:06.750
LOST BOYS GONNA BE SACKED OUT
IN THE LIVING ROOM?

08:06.750 --> 08:07.750
- YOU SAID THEY
COULD STAY HERE.

08:07.750 --> 08:09.168
- YEAH, FOR ONE NIGHT.

08:09.168 --> 08:10.168
ALL RIGHT, KICK 'EM
TO THE CURB,

08:10.168 --> 08:11.208
THIS ISN'T AN ORPHANAGE.

08:11.208 --> 08:12.208
- WHEN ARE WE GONNA
GO VISIT FIONA?

08:12.208 --> 08:15.876
- IT'S THREE HOURS AWAY.

08:15.876 --> 08:17.792
EACH WAY.

08:17.792 --> 08:19.542
HOW THE HELL ARE WE SUPPOSED
TO GET DOWN THERE?

08:19.542 --> 08:21.250
- BUS.
- BORROW YOUR GIRLFRIEND'S CAR.

08:21.250 --> 08:23.041
- NO, LOOK.
I'M BEHIND ON A PHYSICS LAB.

08:23.041 --> 08:25.001
I'VE GOT WORK-STUDY SHIFTS
TO MAKE UP

08:25.001 --> 08:27.625
AND A PAPER DUE IN LIT.

08:27.625 --> 08:30.625
OKAY, THIS WEEKEND.

08:30.625 --> 08:32.126
YOU KNOW, JESUS, GUYS.

08:32.126 --> 08:33.500
IT'S 90 DAYS
IN COUNTRY CLUB JAIL.

08:33.500 --> 08:35.166
ALL RIGHT,
IT'S NOT GUANTANAMO.

08:35.166 --> 08:38.084
OKAY, SHE'S PROBABLY
LEARNING A USEFUL TRADE,

08:38.084 --> 08:40.709
BRUSHING UP ON HER SPANISH.

08:40.709 --> 08:43.126
[buzz]

08:43.126 --> 08:46.126
[indistinct chatter]

09:18.625 --> 09:20.333
- CLEAR.

09:20.333 --> 09:26.208
[indistinct chatter]

09:27.458 --> 09:28.917
- HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

09:28.917 --> 09:31.042
- IT'S NOT MY BIRTHDAY.

09:31.042 --> 09:32.709
- I GOT YOU
A LITTLE PRESENT ANYWAY.

09:32.709 --> 09:36.084
MAKE THE DAY GO EASY.

09:50.168 --> 09:51.168
[car chirps]

09:51.168 --> 09:54.166
[rock music]

09:54.166 --> 09:57.042
♪ ♪

09:57.042 --> 10:00.168
- COME ON, GUYS.

10:00.168 --> 10:01.834
- YO, CARL.

10:01.834 --> 10:03.125
WE TAKING ALL THEM
TO SCHOOL TOO?

10:03.125 --> 10:05.333
- NO, BACK TO THE PARKING LOT
WHERE THEY LIVE.

10:05.333 --> 10:06.500
- WHAT, THEY LIVE
IN A PARKING LOT?

10:06.500 --> 10:08.125
- VAN, BUT IT'S
IN A PARKING LOT.

10:08.125 --> 10:09.667
- WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
WITH CHUCKIE?

10:09.667 --> 10:10.834
- I HAVE TO TAKE HIM
BACK TO THE HOSPITAL

10:10.834 --> 10:12.084
TO SEE HIS MOM AND FRANK.

10:12.084 --> 10:13.876
- WE'RE NOT ALL GONNA FIT.

10:13.876 --> 10:15.917
- SURE WE WILL.

10:15.917 --> 10:17.208
- DO YOU OWN A SUIT?

10:17.208 --> 10:18.417
- A SUIT?

10:18.417 --> 10:19.542
- PREFERABLY BLACK.

10:19.542 --> 10:21.000
- WHY, ARE WE GOING
TO A FUNERAL?

10:21.000 --> 10:23.208
- WORSE--PINNING CEREMONY
AT MY SORORITY.

10:23.208 --> 10:24.458
- WHAT?
- YOU KNOW,

10:24.458 --> 10:27.250
WHITE DRESSES,
CHANTING, CANDLES.

10:27.250 --> 10:28.208
DO YOU OWN A SUIT OR NOT?

10:28.208 --> 10:30.667
- UH, NO.
NO, NOT.

10:30.667 --> 10:33.000
- WELL, THEN I GUESS
WE BETTER GET YOU ONE.

10:36.084 --> 10:37.292
[engine starts]

11:28.542 --> 11:31.417
- SO YOU ARE RAINBOW BOY NOW?

11:31.417 --> 11:33.208
- THE FUCK YOU DO
TO YOUR HAIR?

11:33.208 --> 11:34.667
- YOU WEAR PINK SWEATERS AND

11:34.667 --> 11:36.667
STINK OF MAN PERFUME NOW?

11:36.667 --> 11:39.083
- I LOOK SHITTY IN PINK.

11:42.667 --> 11:44.083
WHAT THE FUCK?

11:44.083 --> 11:45.625
- YOU LIKE THE PENIS, YES?

11:45.625 --> 11:47.166
- NOT WHEN THERE'S TITS
DIRECTLY ABOVE IT.

11:47.166 --> 11:48.542
- YOU WANT IT UP
IN YOUR POOP PLACE?

11:48.542 --> 11:50.125
- NO, I DON'T--
I WANT YOU--FUCKING--

11:50.125 --> 11:51.375
I WANT YOU TO
PUT IT AWAY.

11:51.375 --> 11:52.542
CAN YOU PUT THAT AWAY?

11:52.542 --> 11:55.041
PUT THAT FUCKING
THING AWAY, PLEASE.

12:01.876 --> 12:03.876
THANK YOU.

12:06.042 --> 12:08.917
- YOU LOVE HIM?

12:08.917 --> 12:10.208
- MAYBE.

12:10.208 --> 12:11.876
I DON'T KNOW.

12:11.876 --> 12:14.042
- BECAUSE HE HAS
A REAL PENIS?

12:14.042 --> 12:17.250
- YEAH, I GUESS.

12:22.458 --> 12:24.917
- I HATE THE PENIS.

12:24.917 --> 12:27.333
UGLY FUCKING SKIN STICK.

12:27.333 --> 12:29.834
ALWAYS TRYING TO GET IN
WHERE IT DOESN'T BELONG.

12:29.834 --> 12:31.209
YOU LIKE BOYS.

12:31.209 --> 12:34.084
MAYBE I LIKE GIRLS.

12:34.084 --> 12:35.208
NO PENIS IS STARING AT YOU,

12:35.208 --> 12:38.084
HOPING TO EXPLODE LIKE
STICKY VOLCANO.

12:38.084 --> 12:41.168
AMERICA--
IT'S LAND OF CHOICES, YES?

12:41.168 --> 12:42.500
FREEDOM TO BE ME.

12:42.500 --> 12:44.125
FREEDOM TO BE YOU.

12:44.125 --> 12:46.417
MCDONALD'S, BURGER KING
ON SAME BLOCK.

12:46.417 --> 12:49.500
YOU CHOOSE.
ONE, BOTH.

12:49.500 --> 12:52.084
SHIT, MAYBE WE GO
TO WENDY'S INSTEAD.

12:52.084 --> 12:53.917
- HOLD--YOU'RE A LESBIAN?

12:53.917 --> 12:56.500
- MAYBE YES, MAYBE NO.

12:56.500 --> 12:58.125
CHOICE.

12:58.125 --> 13:00.125
- MORNING.

13:03.792 --> 13:04.876
- NIKA FROM TUG SHOP.

13:04.876 --> 13:06.126
SHE WANTS TO
TAKE CARE OF ME.

13:06.126 --> 13:07.417
- THE BLONDE
WITH THE LAZY EYE?

13:07.417 --> 13:09.292
- SHE PLAYS TRUMPET.

13:09.292 --> 13:11.084
STRONG TONGUE.

13:11.084 --> 13:13.126
BUT BABY NO CHOOSE.

13:13.126 --> 13:15.417
BABY IS ME AND BABY IS YOU.

13:15.417 --> 13:18.500
HE HAS NO VOTE,
NO AMERICA.

13:18.500 --> 13:19.876
WE MUST TAKE CARE OF HIM.

13:19.876 --> 13:21.208
NOT JUST ME.

13:21.208 --> 13:23.458
OTHERWISE I WAIT
UNTIL YOU SLEEP,

13:23.458 --> 13:25.250
AND I STAB YOU AND ORANGE BOY
IN THE HEART

13:25.250 --> 13:27.333
WITH SCREWDRIVERS,
AND I WATCH YOU

13:27.333 --> 13:30.041
BLEED UNTIL YOU DIE.

13:30.041 --> 13:31.625
NO MORE BULLSHIT ABOUT BABY.

13:31.625 --> 13:33.000
[baby crying]

13:33.000 --> 13:37.042
YOU HELP.

13:37.042 --> 13:38.876
AND NIKA COMES HERE TO LIVE.

13:43.250 --> 13:46.917
- ON THREE,
LET'S SAY GERONIMO. READY?

13:46.917 --> 13:49.126
AND SARAH, GIVE DADDY FRANK
A KISS.

13:49.126 --> 13:52.667
OH. ONE, TWO, THREE.

13:52.667 --> 13:54.917
all: GERONIMO.

13:54.917 --> 13:56.083
- GOT IT.

13:56.083 --> 13:57.876
OH, THIS WILL BE GOOD 'CAUSE

13:57.876 --> 14:01.084
THE TRIBAL COUNCIL MIGHT
WANT A PICTURE.

14:01.084 --> 14:02.458
LET'S SEE.

14:02.458 --> 14:04.667
- WHAT?
- YOU'RE NOT DEAD.

14:04.667 --> 14:06.000
- YOU DISAPPOINTED?

14:06.000 --> 14:07.458
- YOU HAVE A TUBE
IN YOUR PENIS.

14:07.458 --> 14:09.250
- GO AWAY.
- AND A BIG DIAPER.

14:09.250 --> 14:12.834
- OH, CHUCK,
LEAVE YOUR POP-POPS ALONE.

14:12.834 --> 14:14.166
- POP-POPS?

14:14.166 --> 14:16.709
- ARE YOU OUR DADDY NOW?
both: NO.

14:16.709 --> 14:19.126
- NOT YET, BUT SOON.

14:19.126 --> 14:21.417
JUST A FEW MORE
LEGAL TECHNICALITIES.

14:21.417 --> 14:24.709
WE'VE GOT TO DOT SOME "I"s
AND CROSS SOME "T"s.

14:24.709 --> 14:26.584
- GOT A BIG POO
IN YOUR DIAPER?

14:26.584 --> 14:29.168
- OH, WELL, WELL, THIS LOOKS
LIKE A CONVENTION IN HERE.

14:29.168 --> 14:30.709
AREN'T YOU THE LUCKY ONE
TO HAVE SUCH A BIG,

14:30.709 --> 14:32.083
LOVING FAMILY?

14:32.083 --> 14:33.750
OKAY, UP WE GO.

14:33.750 --> 14:35.125
TIME FOR YOUR MORNING WALK.
- A WALK?

14:35.125 --> 14:38.000
- [gasps]
OH, OKAY. ALL RIGHT.

14:38.000 --> 14:40.000
- UH, THAT SOUNDS
A LITTLE PAINFUL.

14:40.000 --> 14:42.042
CAN I GET A LITTLE SOMETHING
EXTRA FOR THAT?

14:42.042 --> 14:44.084
- UP WE GO.
- OW!

14:44.084 --> 14:46.126
- OKAY.
- OHH, ARE YOU OKAY, DEAR?

14:46.126 --> 14:48.208
- AH, COME ON,
NOT EVEN A PERCOCET?

14:48.208 --> 14:49.208
A COUPLE OF OXYS?

14:49.208 --> 14:51.042
SOMETHING. JESUS!

14:51.042 --> 14:52.834
- ONE FOOT IN FRONT
OF THE OTHER.

14:52.834 --> 14:53.834
LET'S TRY AND MAKE IT
ALL THE WAY DOWN

14:53.834 --> 14:55.168
TO THE GIFT SHOP TODAY.

14:55.168 --> 14:56.333
- HE'S GOT A LOAD
IN THAT DIAPER.

14:56.333 --> 14:59.417
- CHUCK, SHOW YOUR POP-POP
SOME RESPECT.

14:59.417 --> 15:01.375
- PLEASE DON'T CORRECT
MY CHILD.

15:01.375 --> 15:03.417
- WELL, I'M SORRY.
SOMEBODY HAS TO.

15:03.417 --> 15:04.834
- POO'S GONNA RUN
DOWN HIS LEG.

15:04.834 --> 15:08.126
- CHUCKIE, KNOCK IT OFF.
WATCH TV.

15:08.126 --> 15:09.917
I DON'T APPRECIATE YOUR TONE.

15:09.917 --> 15:11.500
- OH, WELL, UM, YOU KNOW,

15:11.500 --> 15:13.083
HE'S MY GRANDSON NOW TOO,

15:13.083 --> 15:15.500
SO I'VE GOT TO
TAKE SOME RESPONSIBILITY.

15:15.500 --> 15:17.084
- HE'S NOT YOUR GRANDSON.

15:17.084 --> 15:20.584
HE'S YOUR WHAT,
STEP-HALF-GRANDSON MAYBE?

15:20.584 --> 15:22.126
AND DAD DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
YOU WERE MARRIED

15:22.126 --> 15:24.042
UNTIL AN HOUR AGO.
- LET'S SEE.

15:24.042 --> 15:26.584
HOW ABOUT IF WE TALK OUTSIDE
SO WE DON'T BOTHER THE KIDS?

15:26.584 --> 15:28.792
- OKAY.
- WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

15:32.208 --> 15:34.667
TWO MONTHS AGO, HE DIDN'T KNOW
YOU EXISTED.

15:34.667 --> 15:36.208
- HE KNEW I EXISTED.

15:36.208 --> 15:38.126
- AND HE DIDN'T CARE.

15:38.126 --> 15:40.041
I-I DON'T MEAN TO BE CRUEL.

15:40.041 --> 15:41.709
BUT I THINK
IT'S TIME FOR YOU

15:41.709 --> 15:45.041
TO START THINKING ABOUT
YOUR OWN LIFE.

15:45.041 --> 15:46.250
LIKE, WHERE ARE YOU GONNA LIVE?
- GUYS, WATCH OUT, PLEASE.

15:46.250 --> 15:48.959
- WHAT?
WAIT. WHAT?

15:48.959 --> 15:50.250
- YOU'VE BEEN LIVING
AT MY HOUSE,

15:50.250 --> 15:54.168
EATING MY FOOD,
AND SELLING MY FURNITURE.

15:54.168 --> 15:56.041
WITH OUR NEW FAMILY,
THERE JUST

15:56.041 --> 15:58.084
ISN'T ENOUGH ROOM
AT THE INN.

15:58.084 --> 16:00.126
- YOU'RE THROWING US OUT?

16:00.126 --> 16:02.125
- WELL, WE'RE GOING,
ALL OF US,

16:02.125 --> 16:05.209
TO THE ADOPTION HEARING
AT THE RESERVATION TONIGHT.

16:05.209 --> 16:09.042
AND WHEN WE COME BACK,
I WOULD APPRECIATE IT

16:09.042 --> 16:12.208
IF YOU WERE NO LONGER
LIVING AT MY HOUSE.

16:12.208 --> 16:16.625
AND I FORGIVE YOU
FOR SELLING THE FURNITURE.

16:16.625 --> 16:20.041
[machinery whirring]

16:37.001 --> 16:38.208
- SHIT!

16:38.208 --> 16:40.208
FUCK!

16:46.126 --> 16:49.584
WHAT?

16:49.584 --> 16:51.667
WHAT?

17:14.417 --> 17:16.917
NOW?
- YEP.

17:16.917 --> 17:20.126
- I HAVEN'T TAKEN ANYTHING.

17:24.667 --> 17:27.876
- LEAVE IT OPEN.

17:40.250 --> 17:43.001
- [sighs]

17:46.041 --> 17:48.083
[door opens]

18:00.042 --> 18:03.667
- YOU STAYING OUT
OF TROUBLE?

18:03.667 --> 18:05.042
- YES.

18:05.042 --> 18:06.333
- AND YOU GOING
TO YOUR N.A. MEETINGS?

18:06.333 --> 18:07.792
- I'M NOT A DRUG ADDICT.

18:07.792 --> 18:11.333
- THAT'S NOT WHAT I ASKED.
- YES.

18:11.333 --> 18:14.166
- AND YOU'RE CLEAN?

18:14.166 --> 18:18.209
- YES.

18:18.209 --> 18:20.001
- SO I'M NOT GONNA
FIND NOTHING IN THAT CUP

18:20.001 --> 18:23.042
THAT MAKES ME UNHAPPY?

18:25.792 --> 18:27.792
- NOPE.

18:31.584 --> 18:34.667
- LET'S FIND OUT.

18:50.834 --> 18:52.667
- HEY, MAN.
IT'S NOON.

18:52.667 --> 18:54.500
RISE AND FUCKING SHINE,
CINDERELLA.

18:54.500 --> 18:57.667
I'M HEADING TO TOMMY'S
TO GET A DOG.

18:57.667 --> 19:00.168
MANDY SAID SHE'D WATCH
THE BABY MEAT FOR A WHILE.

19:02.333 --> 19:04.876
YO, SLEEPY-FACE.

19:04.876 --> 19:07.042
GET YOUR ASS UP, MAN.
TIME TO ROLL.

19:08.042 --> 19:10.000
- [mumbles indistinctly]

19:10.000 --> 19:12.166
- WHAT'S THAT, MUMBLES?

19:12.166 --> 19:14.834
COME ON, GET UP.

19:14.834 --> 19:19.168
I'M BUYING.

19:19.168 --> 19:20.959
HEY, YOU OKAY?

19:20.959 --> 19:22.000
FEELING SICK OR SOMETHING?

19:22.000 --> 19:25.333
- LEAVE ME ALONE.

19:25.333 --> 19:26.333
- ALL RIGHT,
YOU WANT ME TO BRING YOU

19:26.333 --> 19:28.917
BACK SOMETHING TO EAT?

19:28.917 --> 19:30.000
ALL RIGHT, MAN,
GO FUCK YOURSELF.

19:30.000 --> 19:32.375
SLEEP ALL DAY,
SEE IF I CARE.

19:32.375 --> 19:33.917
- HE OKAY?

19:33.917 --> 19:36.917
- WHO THE FUCK KNOWS?

19:38.917 --> 19:40.584
- YOU'RE A FREAK.
- IT'S TRUE.

19:40.584 --> 19:42.209
IT HAS POWERS.
- BULLSHIT.

19:42.209 --> 19:44.126
HANGING AN UMBILICAL CORD
AROUND YOUR NECK?

19:44.126 --> 19:45.709
- TWO UMBILICAL CORDS.

19:45.709 --> 19:47.250
TWINS--TWICE THE STRENGTH.

19:47.250 --> 19:49.041
- DOESN'T IT SMELL?
- YES.

19:49.041 --> 19:50.417
- WELL, IT KIND OF SMELLS.

19:50.417 --> 19:52.417
OH, MY BABIES.

19:52.417 --> 19:54.667
MWAH, MWAH.

19:54.667 --> 19:56.584
AND YOU TOO.
[chuckles]

19:59.084 --> 20:00.876
- HEY.
- HEY.

20:00.876 --> 20:02.542
- HEY.
- HOW YOU DOING, MICKEY?

20:02.542 --> 20:05.041
- HOW'S BUSINESS UPSTAIRS?
- IT'S SLOW.

20:05.041 --> 20:08.000
YOU KNOW, IT'S--
IT'S COLD OUT.

20:13.292 --> 20:18.417
- HOW'S BUSINESS DOWNSTAIRS,
MICK?

20:18.417 --> 20:20.917
- THAT A FUCKIN' GAY JOKE?

20:20.917 --> 20:22.000
- I DON'T KNOW.
WAS IT FUNNY?

20:22.000 --> 20:23.834
- NO, IT WASN'T FUNNY.

20:23.834 --> 20:27.458
- THEN, NO,
IT WASN'T A GAY JOKE.

20:27.458 --> 20:29.125
- HEY, IF ANYBODY'S
GOT SOMETHING TO SAY,

20:29.125 --> 20:32.917
FUCKING SAY IT!

20:38.667 --> 20:40.667
- WERE YOU SURPRISED?

20:40.667 --> 20:43.084
'CAUSE I WASN'T SURPRISED.

20:43.084 --> 20:44.125
I MEAN, ROCK HUDSON?

20:44.125 --> 20:46.126
THAT WAS A BIT OF A SHOCK.
ELLEN?

20:46.126 --> 20:48.001
THAT KID FROM
DOOGIE HOWSER, M.D.?

20:48.001 --> 20:49.876
- ELLEN? REALLY?
I HAD THAT ONE.

20:49.876 --> 20:52.001
- YEAH, NO STRAIGHT WOMAN
WEARS ADIDAS.

20:52.001 --> 20:54.250
- ROSIE O'DONNELL,
THAT GOT ME.

20:54.250 --> 20:55.750
SHE LOOKS JUST LIKE
MY SISTER.

20:55.750 --> 20:56.667
- I THOUGHT YOUR SISTER
WAS GAY.

20:56.667 --> 20:58.250
- WASN'T BEFORE ELLEN.

20:58.250 --> 21:00.292
- ELTON JOHN--
CANDLE IN THE WIND.

21:00.292 --> 21:01.959
- THAT DIVER
FROM THE UNDERWEAR ADS?

21:01.959 --> 21:03.876
- MARKY MARK?
- MARKY MARK'S NOT GAY.

21:03.876 --> 21:05.417
- HE DID UNDERWEAR ADS.
- NO, NO.

21:05.417 --> 21:07.667
GREG LOUGANIS.
YEAH, HE BUSTED HIS HEAD

21:07.667 --> 21:08.876
ON THE OLYMPIC DIVING BOARD.

21:08.876 --> 21:10.292
BLOOD EVERYWHERE,
KEPT GOING.

21:10.292 --> 21:12.083
TOUGH FUCKER.
- THAT NBA PLAYER LAST YEAR.

21:12.083 --> 21:13.250
- YEAH, JASON COLLINS.

21:13.250 --> 21:14.709
THAT TOOK GUTS.

21:14.709 --> 21:15.917
WHAT ABOUT THAT KID
THAT JUST CAME OUT

21:15.917 --> 21:17.250
IN COLLEGE FOOTBALL,
MICHAEL SAM?

21:17.250 --> 21:19.250
- FERGIE.
- NO SHIT. FERGIE?

21:19.250 --> 21:22.292
- WELL, MAYBE JUST BISEXUAL,
BUT STILL.

21:29.084 --> 21:32.208
- MICKEY, HAVE A SEAT, MAN.

21:32.208 --> 21:35.542
NO ONE GIVES A SHIT
WHO YOU BANG.

21:35.542 --> 21:38.250
LET ME BUY YOU A BEER.

21:42.168 --> 21:43.834
TO BUTT BUDDIES,

21:43.834 --> 21:46.250
LONG MAY THEY
SLAM AND SLAP.

21:46.250 --> 21:49.250
all: TO BUTT BUDDIES.

21:51.959 --> 21:53.709
- WHO ELSE?

21:53.709 --> 21:56.250
- HOW'S IT GOING IN THERE?

21:56.250 --> 21:57.959
LIP?

21:57.959 --> 21:59.417
- YEAH?
- COME ON OUT.

21:59.417 --> 22:01.584
LET ME SEE.

22:05.375 --> 22:08.250
UH, SHOULDERS AND LAPELS.

22:08.250 --> 22:11.001
ARE WE HAPPY
WITH THESE LAPELS?

22:11.001 --> 22:12.042
IS THIS THE ARMANI?

22:12.042 --> 22:14.458
- PAUL SMITH.

22:14.458 --> 22:17.125
- LET'S TRY THE PRADA.
- OKAY.

22:19.876 --> 22:21.333
- STOP FIDGETING.

22:21.333 --> 22:23.208
- JESUS CHRIST.

22:23.208 --> 22:24.667
- YOU'LL WEAR IT FOR YEARS.

22:24.667 --> 22:27.333
- I FEEL A BIT
LIKE, UH, PRETTY WOMAN.

22:27.333 --> 22:28.750
- PRETTY BOY.

22:28.750 --> 22:31.126
- KEPT BOY.
- BOY TOY, THEN.

22:31.126 --> 22:32.126
- WHAT, THAT'S BETTER?

22:32.126 --> 22:33.125
- I WANT ALL THOSE BITCHES

22:33.125 --> 22:34.792
AT THE SORORITY SUICIDAL
WITH ENVY.

22:34.792 --> 22:36.250
- OH, THAT'S WHAT
THIS IS ABOUT.

22:36.250 --> 22:37.584
- WHY NOT?

22:37.584 --> 22:39.042
IS THERE ANYTHING ON EARTH

22:39.042 --> 22:42.084
MORE ENJOYABLE THAN
HUMILIATING YOUR PEERS?

22:44.042 --> 22:46.166
GO, GO.

22:46.166 --> 22:48.126
- OKAY.

22:48.126 --> 22:50.083
- YUMMY.

22:50.083 --> 22:54.584
[machinery whirring]

23:01.166 --> 23:03.375
- LET'S GO.

23:07.041 --> 23:08.667
- WHERE'S MS. JOHNSON?

23:08.667 --> 23:10.792
- YOU'RE WITH ME.

23:10.792 --> 23:13.792
- I DIDN'T TAKE IT, BITCH.

23:20.209 --> 23:21.792
I HAVEN'T DONE ANY DRUGS.

23:21.792 --> 23:23.667
OKAY, IF SOMETHING SHOWED UP
IN THAT TEST,

23:23.667 --> 23:25.126
THEN THERE WAS SOMETHING WRONG
WITH THE TEST,

23:25.126 --> 23:28.083
OR SOMEBODY PUT SOMETHING
IN MY FOOD OR SOMETHING.

23:29.709 --> 23:31.000
THERE'S A WOMAN HERE.

23:31.000 --> 23:32.333
SHE'S BEEN GIVING ME
A LOT OF SHIT.

23:32.333 --> 23:34.500
- GET YOUR STUFF.
YOU'RE OUT.

23:40.041 --> 23:42.417
- [deep breath]

23:54.126 --> 23:56.042
[car door opens]

23:58.876 --> 24:01.792
- GET IN THE CAR.

24:04.126 --> 24:06.458
COLD OUT HERE.

24:12.458 --> 24:14.458
SEAT BELT.

24:18.126 --> 24:20.041
HUNGRY?

24:20.041 --> 24:22.083
THERE'S A SONIC
OFF THE HIGHWAY.

24:22.083 --> 24:24.125
WE'LL STOP
AND GET YOU SOMETHING.

24:24.125 --> 24:27.083
[engine starts]

24:30.625 --> 24:32.333
- WE HAVE
DEFLATED THE BALLOON,

24:32.333 --> 24:34.292
AND WE ARE NOW READY TO

24:34.292 --> 24:36.041
REMOVE THE CATHETER
FROM THE URETHRA.

24:36.041 --> 24:37.417
- CHUCKIE, COME ON.

24:37.417 --> 24:38.876
- YOU MIGHT
FEEL SOME DISCOMFORT

24:38.876 --> 24:41.126
AS THE BALLOON PASSES
THROUGH THE MEATUS.

24:41.126 --> 24:42.208
- "THE MEATUS."

24:42.208 --> 24:43.750
I THINK HE MEANS MY DICK.

24:43.750 --> 24:45.000
- GIVE ME A BIG EXHALE.

24:45.000 --> 24:46.667
- DON'T YOU NORMALLY
KNOCK PEOPLE--

24:46.667 --> 24:48.500
AAH!
[panting]

24:48.500 --> 24:50.250
- ALL DONE.

24:50.250 --> 24:51.834
NOW, LET'S GET
THOSE STAPLES OUT.

24:51.834 --> 24:54.084
TURN ON YOUR SIDE.

24:54.084 --> 24:55.667
- CHUCKIE, NO.

24:55.667 --> 24:57.250
- WE'VE STARTED YOU
ON A COURSE OF...

24:57.250 --> 24:59.333
- COME ON, THAT'S DIRTY.
- IMMUNOSUPPRESSIVE NEORAL,

24:59.333 --> 25:00.333
WHICH YOU'LL NEED
TO CONTINUE

25:00.333 --> 25:02.375
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE,

25:02.375 --> 25:05.667
TO AVOID
REJECTING YOUR TRANSPLANT.

25:05.667 --> 25:07.584
THERE ARE A FEW SIDE EFFECTS.

25:07.584 --> 25:10.083
HIGH BLOOD PRESSURE,
HAND TREMORS,

25:10.083 --> 25:12.333
HEADACHES,
INCREASED HAIR GROWTH,

25:12.333 --> 25:14.126
SWOLLEN GUMS, NIGHT SWEATS,

25:14.126 --> 25:17.792
AND AN ELEVATED CHANCE
OF DEPRESSION.

25:17.792 --> 25:19.084
YOU'LL ALSO BE
ON PREDNISONE.

25:19.084 --> 25:21.000
- DOES THAT HAVE
A DR. FRANKENSTEIN LIST

25:21.000 --> 25:22.375
OF SIDE EFFECTS, TOO?

25:22.375 --> 25:25.292
- STOMACH ULCERS,
ACNE, CATARACTS,

25:25.292 --> 25:28.333
GLAUCOMA,
DIARRHEA, NIGHTMARES,

25:28.333 --> 25:30.500
INSOMNIA, MORE HAIR GROWTH.

25:30.500 --> 25:32.041
- WHAT ABOUT
A LITTLE SOMETHING

25:32.041 --> 25:33.083
TO TAKE THE EDGE OFF?

25:33.083 --> 25:34.500
WHAT ABOUT PAIN MEDS?

25:34.500 --> 25:37.458
- TYLENOL WORKS WELL
FOR DISCOMFORT.

25:37.458 --> 25:41.625
YOU ARE AT INCREASED DANGER
OF INFECTION,

25:41.625 --> 25:44.041
SO BATHE REGULARLY
AND WASH YOUR HANDS.

25:44.041 --> 25:46.125
- WHEN CAN I DRINK?

25:46.125 --> 25:48.458
- ALCOHOL?
YOU CAN'T.

25:48.458 --> 25:49.375
- WHAT?

25:49.375 --> 25:51.292
- ALCOHOL STRESSES THE LIVER

25:51.292 --> 25:54.000
AND CAN DILUTE
YOUR ANTI-REJECTION MEDS.

25:54.000 --> 25:56.083
- WELL, WHAT'S THE POINT
OF GETTING A NEW LIVER

25:56.083 --> 25:58.417
IF THE DAMN THING WON'T
DO WHAT IT'S DESIGNED TO DO?

25:58.417 --> 26:01.166
- TRY NEAR BEER.
IT'S SURPRISINGLY TASTY,

26:01.166 --> 26:03.959
AND ENJOYED BY MILLIONS
OF RETIRED ALCOHOLICS,

26:03.959 --> 26:05.959
ME INCLUDED.

26:08.333 --> 26:11.084
- HE DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING
ABOUT POT.

26:16.709 --> 26:18.417
- [grunts, whimpers]

26:18.417 --> 26:21.168
[knock at door]

26:21.168 --> 26:23.250
- I'LL GET IT.

26:25.000 --> 26:27.500
HI.
- HI.

26:27.500 --> 26:29.209
DID YOU ORDER A PIZZA?

26:29.209 --> 26:31.208
- EXTRA LARGE, CHEESY CRUST
WITH PEPPERONCINI?

26:31.208 --> 26:32.417
- UH, YEAH.

26:32.417 --> 26:34.834
- THIS MUST
BE THE PLACE THEN.

26:34.834 --> 26:36.250
- OKAY.

26:36.250 --> 26:37.876
- FOOD!

26:37.876 --> 26:39.625
HOW MUCH?

26:39.625 --> 26:41.667
- UH, $16.50.

26:41.667 --> 26:42.834
- HERE'S 20.

26:42.834 --> 26:44.000
- OH.
- KEEP THE CHANGE.

26:44.000 --> 26:45.000
I'LL GET MY COAT,
AND WE CAN GO.

26:45.000 --> 26:47.042
- OH. UH, GO?

26:47.042 --> 26:49.042
I'M--I'M KIND OF WORKING.
- I KNOW.

26:49.042 --> 26:50.417
I NEED A RIDE TO
THE CHECK-CASHING PLACE

26:50.417 --> 26:53.458
ON CERMAK AND
THE GAS COMPANY ON 67TH.

26:53.458 --> 26:55.084
PIZZA'S HERE.

26:55.084 --> 26:56.083
I'LL BE BACK
IN AN HOUR OR SO.

26:56.083 --> 26:59.500
I HAVE TO GO PAY SOME BILLS.

26:59.500 --> 27:01.168
- IT'S NICE IN HERE NOW.

27:01.168 --> 27:02.959
I DON'T HAVE TO WEAR MY PARKA
INSIDE ANYMORE.

27:02.959 --> 27:04.667
- DEBBIE SAID WE COULD
TURN UP THE HEAT.

27:04.667 --> 27:07.084
WANT ME TO GET US SOME PIZZA?
- I'M NOT HUNGRY.

27:07.084 --> 27:08.750
- THAT WAS FUNNY
AT ASSEMBLY TODAY

27:08.750 --> 27:10.458
WHEN THAT CHICK THREW UP.
- YEAH.

27:10.458 --> 27:12.333
SOME KIDS JUST CAN'T
HOLD THEIR JAGER.

27:12.333 --> 27:14.168
- YOU HEAR ANYTHING
FROM YOUR MOM?

27:14.168 --> 27:15.375
- SHE'LL BE BACK.

27:15.375 --> 27:16.667
SHE NEVER STAYS AWAY
FOR MORE THAN,

27:16.667 --> 27:19.208
LIKE, A NIGHT OR TWO.

27:19.208 --> 27:21.208
- WANT TO SPEND THE NIGHT
HERE AGAIN?

27:21.208 --> 27:23.209
- I THOUGHT YOUR BROTHER SAID
HE DIDN'T WANT US AROUND.

27:23.209 --> 27:25.876
- IT'S MY HOUSE TOO.

27:25.876 --> 27:28.625
I GOT YOU SOMETHING.

27:31.417 --> 27:33.709
- YOU BOUGHT ME THAT?

27:33.709 --> 27:37.792
- STOLE, BUT YEAH.

27:37.792 --> 27:39.000
- YOU'RE NOT STARTING
TO LIKE ME

27:39.000 --> 27:42.084
OR ANYTHING, ARE YOU?

27:42.084 --> 27:43.292
- LIKE YOU?

27:43.292 --> 27:45.834
- LIKE, FALL IN LOVE
OR ANYTHING WEIRD?

27:45.834 --> 27:47.042
- NO.

27:47.042 --> 27:49.042
- GOOD, DON'T.

27:49.042 --> 27:51.168
- WHY NOT?

27:51.168 --> 27:53.834
- JUST DON'T.

27:53.834 --> 27:55.083
I SHOULD GET BACK
TO THE VAN,

27:55.083 --> 27:56.542
IN CASE MOM SHOWS UP.

27:56.542 --> 27:58.542
THANKS FOR THE BEER.

28:04.667 --> 28:06.625
COME ON, GUYS.
TIME TO GO.

28:06.625 --> 28:09.500
TIME TO GO.
LET'S GO.

28:14.333 --> 28:17.333
- YOU KNOW WHY YOU OUT?

28:17.333 --> 28:19.333
- NO, BUT THANK YOU.

28:19.333 --> 28:21.041
- YEAH, DON'T THANK ME.
IT WASN'T ME.

28:21.041 --> 28:22.917
OVERCROWDING.

28:22.917 --> 28:25.125
NON-VIOLENT OFFENDERS
ROTATE OUT

28:25.125 --> 28:28.208
AFTER 10% TO 20% TIME SERVED.

28:33.667 --> 28:35.208
SO WHAT SENT YOU
ON THAT BENDER,

28:35.208 --> 28:38.001
MADE YOU BUST
YOUR PROBATION?

28:38.001 --> 28:39.458
- I DON'T KNOW.

28:39.458 --> 28:41.292
MAYBE IT JUST GOT TOO HARD.

28:41.292 --> 28:42.792
- LETTING YOURSELF OFF
A LITTLE EASY,

28:42.792 --> 28:44.083
DON'T YOU THINK?
- I WENT BACK TO JAIL.

28:44.083 --> 28:45.250
THERE'S NOTHING EASY
ABOUT THAT.

28:45.250 --> 28:46.876
- SURE IT IS.
THE HARD PART IS

28:46.876 --> 28:47.876
STAYING OUT AND CLEAN.

28:47.876 --> 28:48.876
RELAPSING IS EASY.

28:48.876 --> 28:50.417
- I'M NOT A DRUG ADDICT.

28:50.417 --> 28:51.876
- YEAH, SO YOU KEEP SAYING.
- IT'S THE TRUTH.

28:51.876 --> 28:54.042
- THEN WHAT WAS ALL THAT
ABOUT THEN, HUH?

28:54.042 --> 28:56.166
- I HONESTLY DON'T KNOW.

28:56.166 --> 28:58.500
- THEN WHAT'S YOUR SAD STORY?

28:58.500 --> 29:01.083
'CAUSE WE ALL SCREWED UP
IN ONE WAY OR THE OTHER.

29:01.083 --> 29:04.000
NOT MANY WHITE PICKET FENCES
WHERE WE COME FROM.

29:05.667 --> 29:08.001
- YOU'RE SOUTH SIDE?

29:08.001 --> 29:10.209
- BORN AND RAISED.

29:10.209 --> 29:12.166
MY DAD DRANK.

29:12.166 --> 29:16.042
I LOVED HIM,
BUT HE WAS A DRUNK.

29:16.042 --> 29:18.166
BUT YOU A GROWN-UP.

29:18.166 --> 29:19.750
THERE COMES A POINT
IN TIME THAT

29:19.750 --> 29:24.001
YOU GOT TO TAKE CONTROL
OF YOUR OWN LIFE.

29:24.001 --> 29:26.333
WHATEVER YOU FROM,
WHOEVER DID YOU WRONG,

29:26.333 --> 29:28.333
DIDN'T DO WHAT THEY
WERE SUPPOSED TO DO,

29:28.333 --> 29:30.458
WASN'T BEING WHO THEY
WAS SUPPOSED TO BE?

29:30.458 --> 29:32.625
[scoffs]
IT'S JUST YOU.

29:32.625 --> 29:34.458
NO MORE EXCUSES.

29:42.709 --> 29:44.209
- YO, IT'S AFTER 5:00.

29:44.209 --> 29:46.792
YOU TRYING TO SET
SOME SORT OF RECORD?

29:46.792 --> 29:48.375
YOU'RE NOT STILL SLEEPING.
GET UP.

29:48.375 --> 29:52.084
- LEAVE ME ALONE.

29:52.084 --> 29:53.166
- IAN, ARE YOU HIGH?

29:53.166 --> 29:54.209
YOU TAKE SOMETHING?

29:54.209 --> 29:56.084
- [whispers]
GO AWAY.

29:56.084 --> 29:57.250
- OKAY, YOU WANT ME TO

29:57.250 --> 29:58.500
CALL THE CLUB AT LEAST
AND TELL THEM--

29:58.500 --> 30:01.458
- JESUS! LEAVE ME ALONE!

30:11.333 --> 30:14.333
- FUCK'S WRONG WITH HIM?

30:23.500 --> 30:25.959
- AND IN CONCLUSION,

30:25.959 --> 30:29.041
I FEEL MY HUSBAND
AND I CAN PROVIDE A WARM,

30:29.041 --> 30:32.208
INCLUSIVE,
NURTURING ENVIRONMENT

30:32.208 --> 30:35.417
THAT VALIDATES
THE CULTURAL IDENTITY

30:35.417 --> 30:39.917
OF OUR SHARED
NATIVE AMERICAN HERITAGE.

30:39.917 --> 30:41.001
THANK YOU.

30:41.001 --> 30:43.084
[mic feedback]

30:46.041 --> 30:47.792
- THANK YOU,
MRS. GALLAGHER.

30:47.792 --> 30:49.041
I'M SURE I SPEAK
FOR ALL OF US

30:49.041 --> 30:51.542
WHEN I SAY WE
APPRECIATE THE DILIGENCE

30:51.542 --> 30:53.542
YOU HAVE SHOWN IN CARING
FOR THESE CHILDREN.

30:53.542 --> 30:59.041
- [speaks native language]

30:59.041 --> 31:00.458
- WELL, THEN, I SPEAK
FOR MOST OF US

31:00.458 --> 31:02.792
WHEN I SAY YOUR DEVOTION
IS VERY IMPRESSIVE.

31:02.792 --> 31:07.375
[all speaking native language]

31:07.375 --> 31:11.417
- GARY, WHAT ARE THEY SAYING?

31:11.417 --> 31:12.876
- I DON'T KNOW.

31:12.876 --> 31:15.417
I'M TAKING CHINESE.

31:15.417 --> 31:17.292
