31:45.709 --> 31:48.333
- NO.

31:48.333 --> 31:49.667
- NO WHAT?

31:49.667 --> 31:52.041
- YOU CANNOT
ADOPT THE CHILDREN.

31:52.041 --> 31:53.917
THEIR GRANDFATHER
WILL TAKE THEM.

31:53.917 --> 31:55.292
- GRANDFATHER?

31:55.292 --> 31:57.750
- [speaking native language]

31:57.750 --> 31:59.000
- GREAT-GRANDFATHER.

31:59.000 --> 32:01.001
- [speaking native language]

32:01.001 --> 32:03.292
- WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME
YOU HAD A GRANDFATHER?

32:03.292 --> 32:05.792
- HE DOESN'T HAVE WI-FI.

32:05.792 --> 32:11.709
- [speaking native language]

32:19.500 --> 32:22.333
[speaking native language]

32:28.083 --> 32:30.375
- THE MENOMINEE NATION
THANKS YOU FOR YOUR CARE

32:30.375 --> 32:32.000
OF THESE CHILDREN
AND WOULD LIKE TO OFFER YOU

32:32.000 --> 32:35.250
