34:05.000 --> 34:06.625
- NOT YET.

34:06.625 --> 34:08.250
- N.A. OR A.A.?

34:08.250 --> 34:12.208
- N.A. AL-ANON TOO,
I'M GUESSING.

34:12.208 --> 34:14.542
- I GOT A MEETING DOWN
THE STREET AT THE EPISCOPAL.

34:14.542 --> 34:16.166
