34:16.166 --> 34:18.125
JACKIE.

34:21.126 --> 34:23.250
JACKIE SCAVELLO,
FIONA GALLAGHER.

34:23.250 --> 34:25.750
YOU TAKE HER IN THE BACK,
SET HER UP WITH A LOCKER,

34:25.750 --> 34:27.084
