37:56.042 --> 37:58.500
- UH, NO, THE CHANTING PART
WAS KIND OF CREEPY.

37:58.500 --> 38:00.125
BUT HEY, I LOOK GOOD
IN A SUIT, RIGHT?

38:00.125 --> 38:02.333
YOU KNOW, I FIGURED
IT WAS GONNA BE MORE

38:02.333 --> 38:04.959
WILD TOGA PARTY THAN COVEN.

38:04.959 --> 38:06.792
- WELL, WE'RE A BUNCH
OF ENGINEERING MAJORS.

38:06.792 --> 38:09.001
OUR PARTIES USUALLY
CONSIST OF US

38:09.001 --> 38:10.625
WATCHING BIG BANG  RERUNS

38:10.625 --> 38:12.876
AND BLEACHING EACH OTHER'S
MUSTACHES.

38:12.876 --> 38:14.458
- EVERYBODY WANT COFFEE?
- OH, YES, PLEASE.

38:14.458 --> 38:16.125
- YEAH.
- OKAY, GREAT.

38:16.125 --> 38:18.584
WE'VE GOT A SPECIAL
ON THE TODDLE HOUSE BREAKFAST.

38:18.584 --> 38:20.625
IT'S A HAM AND CHEESE OMELET.

38:20.625 --> 38:24.792
IT'S GOT SAUSAGE
OR BACON, GRITS--

38:24.792 --> 38:28.709
GRITS, UM,
WITH A CHOICE OF TOAST,

38:28.709 --> 38:30.876
AND IT'S 4.99.

38:30.876 --> 38:33.709
OKAY, I'LL BE BACK
TO TAKE YOUR ORDER.

38:38.667 --> 38:41.667
- EXCUSE ME, I JUST
GOT TO GO TAKE A LEAK.

38:46.001 --> 38:48.041
MANDY, HEY.

38:48.041 --> 38:50.834
- YOU WANT SOME
MORE COFFEE, SIR?

38:50.834 --> 38:53.625
- UH, NO, NO.

38:53.625 --> 38:54.750
UM, HEY, LOOK.

38:54.750 --> 38:56.417
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WORKED HERE.

38:56.417 --> 38:59.001
- I'LL BE WITH YOUR TABLE
IN JUST A MINUTE.

39:03.168 --> 39:06.417
- YOU LOOK GREAT.

39:06.417 --> 39:08.125
- YOU WANT SOMETHING ELSE?

39:08.125 --> 39:10.209
MORE SUGAR?

39:10.209 --> 39:12.917
CREAM?

39:14.542 --> 39:18.084
- NO, UH...

39:18.084 --> 39:21.209
NO, WE'RE GOOD.

39:21.209 --> 39:24.000
THANK YOU.

39:28.166 --> 39:29.625
- I'M STARVING.

39:29.625 --> 39:32.292
- ME TOO.
I LOVE TEXAS TOAST.

39:32.292 --> 39:34.292
- WHAT'S TEXAS TOAST?
- THANKS.

39:35.792 --> 39:37.042
- YOU KNOW THE WAITRESS?

39:37.042 --> 39:39.126
- OH, I THOUGHT
I DID FROM SCHOOL.

39:39.126 --> 39:40.834
[indistinct chatter]

39:40.834 --> 39:44.041
- DID YOU GUYS SEE
KAREN'S DRESS TONIGHT?

39:44.041 --> 39:45.417
- WAFFLES?

39:45.417 --> 39:47.292
- DO THEY JUST HAVE FRUIT?

39:47.292 --> 39:49.042
- SO WHAT ARE
YOU GUYS THINKING, HUH?

39:49.042 --> 39:50.625
[indistinct chatter]

39:50.625 --> 39:52.917
- UM...

39:52.917 --> 39:56.041
HOW ABOUT THE MEGA-OMELET?

39:56.041 --> 39:57.876
- YEAH.

