42:27.084 --> 42:28.834
- [sighs]

42:31.458 --> 42:34.458
HI.

42:38.250 --> 42:43.458
[silverware rattling]

42:53.542 --> 42:55.375
[exhales]

42:59.584 --> 43:00.792
FIONA.

43:00.792 --> 43:02.209
- HI.

43:02.209 --> 43:05.126
I'M MAKING FRENCH TOAST.

43:05.126 --> 43:07.084
- [crying]

43:07.084 --> 43:08.209
- OH, JESUS.

43:08.209 --> 43:09.458
ARE YOU CRYING?

43:09.458 --> 43:12.375
OH, DON'T CRY.
I'LL START CRYING TOO.

43:12.375 --> 43:16.375
- [crying]

43:22.625 --> 43:24.458
- [laughs]
HI.

43:24.458 --> 43:26.625
OH!
[laughs]

43:32.041 --> 43:34.209
OKAY, OKAY, ENOUGH.

43:34.209 --> 43:38.126
JESUS, STOP.

43:38.126 --> 43:39.542
[laughs]

43:39.542 --> 43:40.750
SCHOOL, COME ON.

43:40.750 --> 43:43.500
WE'VE GOT TO GET MOVING.

43:43.500 --> 43:47.168
WHAT?

43:47.168 --> 43:49.166
GOD, WHAT?

43:49.166 --> 43:50.250
- YOU WANT TO GET UP?

43:50.250 --> 43:53.417
I'LL MAKE YOU A SANDWICH.

43:53.417 --> 43:55.417
OR I COULD GET MY SNEAKERS
IN THE HOUSE.

43:55.417 --> 43:58.292
WE COULD GO FOR A RUN
AT THE TRACK.

43:58.292 --> 43:59.750
YOU WANT TO GO FOR A RUN?

43:59.750 --> 44:01.667
GET SOME FRESH AIR?

44:01.667 --> 44:03.625
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

44:07.084 --> 44:10.209
OKAY, OKAY.

44:20.292 --> 44:22.042
HOW LONG HAS HE
BEEN LIKE THAT?

44:22.042 --> 44:23.166
- SINCE YESTERDAY MORNING.

44:23.166 --> 44:24.125
- AND HE HASN'T
GOTTEN OUT OF BED?

44:24.125 --> 44:26.209
- NO, HE'S JUST SLEEPING.

44:26.209 --> 44:27.375
I CAN'T GET HIM UP.
I-I TRIED.

44:27.375 --> 44:28.584
- YEAH, SO DID I.

44:28.584 --> 44:30.417
- AND WHAT ABOUT BEFORE?
WHAT WAS HE LIKE?

44:30.417 --> 44:32.041
- BEFORE, HE WAS FINE.
HE WAS HAPPY.

44:32.041 --> 44:33.834
HE'S STAYING UP ALL HOURS
OF THE NIGHT,

44:33.834 --> 44:35.667
DANCING,
TELLING FUCKING JOKES.

44:35.667 --> 44:37.375
HE KICKS MY ASS EVERY DAY.
I CAN'T KEEP UP WITH HIM.

44:37.375 --> 44:38.417
- WE'VE GOT TO GET AHOLD
OF LIP.

44:38.417 --> 44:39.917
HE SHOULD KNOW.

44:39.917 --> 44:41.166
- KNOW WHAT?
WHAT'S WRONG WITH HIM?

44:41.166 --> 44:44.876
- UH, DEPRESSION, I THINK.

44:44.876 --> 44:46.500
- HE--HE'S DEPRESSED?

44:46.500 --> 44:48.168
WHAT DO YOU MEAN HE'S--
WE ALL GET FUCKING DEPRESSED.

44:48.168 --> 44:49.584
HOW THE FUCK COULD WE NOT,
LIVING AROUND HERE?

44:49.584 --> 44:51.542
- IT'S NOT THAT KIND
OF DEPRESSED, OKAY?

44:51.542 --> 44:53.168
LOOK, I COULD BE WRONG,

44:53.168 --> 44:56.959
BUT IT COULD
BE BIPOLAR DISEASE,

44:56.959 --> 44:58.542
LIKE OUR MOM.

44:58.542 --> 45:00.292
- BI--BI--BI-WHAT?
WHAT THE FUCK IS THAT?

45:00.292 --> 45:02.041
- IT'S MANIC DEPRESSION,
MICK.

45:02.041 --> 45:04.500
- IT'S LIKE HIGH HIGHS
FOLLOWED BY LOW LOWS,

45:04.500 --> 45:06.041
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

45:06.041 --> 45:07.458
WE'LL GET HIM AN APPOINTMENT
AT THE CLINIC,

45:07.458 --> 45:08.709
AND WE'LL SEE WHAT THEY SAY.

45:08.709 --> 45:10.209
- NO, NO, LOOK.
HE--HE'S LOW.

45:10.209 --> 45:11.625
WE CHEER HIM UP.
- IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.

45:11.625 --> 45:13.542
HE MAY HAVE TO
BE HOSPITALIZED.

45:13.542 --> 45:17.208
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN, HOS--
LIKE A PSYCH WARD?

45:17.208 --> 45:19.625
NO FUCKING WAY!
NO FUCKING WAY!

45:19.625 --> 45:20.625
HE'S STAYING HERE.

45:20.625 --> 45:22.000
- HE COULD END UP SUICIDAL.

45:22.000 --> 45:24.042
- THEN WE HIDE THE KNIVES
UNTIL HE PERKS UP.

45:24.042 --> 45:25.625
I CAN--I CAN TAKE CARE
OF HIM.

45:25.625 --> 45:27.792
OKAY, LET ME TAKE CARE OF HIM
UNTIL HE'S BETTER.

45:27.792 --> 45:29.209
- IT--IT CAN BE WEEKS.

45:29.209 --> 45:30.667
IT'S MOOD SWINGS, OKAY?

45:30.667 --> 45:32.166
IT'S ALMOST IMPOSSIBLE
TO HANDLE.

45:32.166 --> 45:35.001
- DON'T FUCKING TELL ME
WHAT'S IMPOSSIBLE!

45:35.001 --> 45:36.458
WE'RE TAKING CARE
OF HIM HERE.

45:36.458 --> 45:38.750
YOU, ME, US.

45:38.750 --> 45:41.584
HE'S FUCKING FAMILY.

45:46.292 --> 45:48.126
- I HAVE TO GET
TO A MEETING, OKAY?

45:48.126 --> 45:50.042
UM, WE'LL CALL LIP,

45:50.042 --> 45:51.042
AND WE'LL LET HIM KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON.

45:51.042 --> 45:52.542
OKAY, COME ON.

45:52.542 --> 45:54.417
- HE'S NOT GOING TO
SOME FUCKING NUT HOUSE.

45:54.417 --> 45:56.625
YOU HEAR ME?

45:56.625 --> 45:58.084
HE STAYS HERE.

45:58.084 --> 46:01.001
HE'S STAYING WITH ME.

46:08.834 --> 46:11.209
- HEY. HEY!

46:11.209 --> 46:13.125
YOU SEE A VAN PARKED HERE,

46:13.125 --> 46:15.084
BUNCH OF KIDS
LIVING IN IT?

46:15.084 --> 46:16.500
IT WAS HERE YESTERDAY.

46:16.500 --> 46:17.625
- YEAH. YEAH,
THEY WERE HERE.

46:17.625 --> 46:20.375
MUST HAVE LEFT.

46:20.375 --> 46:23.375
[rock music]

46:23.375 --> 46:31.375
