47:22.166 --> 47:23.500
- MRS. GALLAGHER
HAS REQUESTED THAT

47:23.500 --> 47:24.834
YOU NOT BE ALLOWED
IN THE ROOM.

47:24.834 --> 47:26.584
- HE'S MY DAD.

47:26.584 --> 47:28.083
- SHE'S CONCERNED
THAT YOUR PRESENCE

47:28.083 --> 47:30.250
IS UPSETTING
TO MR. GALLAGHER.

47:30.250 --> 47:32.001
- SHEILA!

47:32.001 --> 47:34.126
SHEILA, GET YOUR FAT ASS
OUT HERE!

47:34.126 --> 47:35.667
- PLEASE, I DON'T WANT
TO HAVE TO CALL SECURITY.

47:35.667 --> 47:38.166
I'M JUST GONNA--
- I'M GONNA FUCK YOU UP!

47:38.166 --> 47:39.876
- CALL SECURITY.
- YOU FUCK WITH THE BULL,

47:39.876 --> 47:42.042
YOU GET AN ASS FULL
OF HORNS!

47:42.042 --> 47:43.625
- KEEP YOUR VOICE DOWN.

47:43.625 --> 47:45.876
- YOU CAN'T KEEP ME AWAY
FROM MY DAD.

47:45.876 --> 47:48.084
- HE IS MY HUSBAND.

47:48.084 --> 47:50.001
- I'M HIS BLOOD.
- I'M HIS WIFE.

47:50.001 --> 47:51.667
- YOU'VE GOT YOUR KIDS.
HE'S THE ONLY FAMILY I'VE GOT.

47:51.667 --> 47:53.625
- NO, I LOST THE KIDS.

47:53.625 --> 47:55.458
THE TRIBE WOULDN'T
LET ME ADOPT THEM.

47:55.458 --> 47:58.333
- OH, I'M SO SORRY.

47:58.333 --> 48:00.084
SO NOW YOU HAVE ROOM FOR US
AT YOUR HOUSE.

48:00.084 --> 48:01.000
- [gasps]

48:01.000 --> 48:02.584
- LET ME SEE MY FATHER,
YOU BITCH.

48:02.584 --> 48:04.375
- NO!

48:04.375 --> 48:05.834
I'M THE ONE HE'S CHOSEN TO

48:05.834 --> 48:07.042
SPEND THE REST
OF HIS LIFE WITH.

48:07.042 --> 48:09.166
YOU'RE JUST ONE LUCKY SPERM.

48:09.166 --> 48:11.209
- OH!
[indistinct chatter]

48:11.209 --> 48:13.208
[screams]
[indistinct chatter]

48:15.959 --> 48:18.168
SHE SAYS I CAN'T
SEE MY DAD!

48:18.168 --> 48:20.667
- [whispering indistinctly]
- MRS. GALLAGHER.

48:20.667 --> 48:22.125
I AM SO SORRY TO--

48:22.125 --> 48:23.792
- SHE JUST ASSAULTED ME!
EVERYONE IN THIS HOSPITAL!

48:23.792 --> 48:26.000
I WAS ASSAULTED!

48:28.625 --> 48:30.000
- HI.

48:30.000 --> 48:33.375
- HEY.

48:33.375 --> 48:35.209
- WHAT'S GOING ON
OUT THERE?

48:35.209 --> 48:37.375
- CATFIGHT--
SAMMI AND SHEILA.

48:37.375 --> 48:38.500
- OVER WHAT?

48:38.500 --> 48:41.792
- YOU, I THINK.

48:41.792 --> 48:43.084
- WHO'S WINNING?

48:43.084 --> 48:44.041
- HARD TO TELL.

48:44.041 --> 48:46.876
MAYBE THE RENT-A-COPS.

48:46.876 --> 48:50.208
YOU READY TO
GET OUT OF HERE?

48:50.208 --> 48:52.458
- ABSOLUTELY.

48:52.458 --> 48:55.458
[upbeat music]

48:55.458 --> 48:58.917
♪ ♪

48:58.917 --> 49:00.834
- LADIES, I NEED YOU
TO KEEP IT DOWN.

49:00.834 --> 49:02.584
- THIS IS AMERICA,
AND IN THIS COUNTRY,

49:02.584 --> 49:05.792
PEOPLE HAVE A RIGHT TO
SEE THEIR FAMILIES.

49:05.792 --> 49:10.458
[indistinct chatter]

49:10.458 --> 49:12.125
- BYE.

49:12.125 --> 49:14.458
[indistinct chatter]

49:14.458 --> 49:16.458
- IT'S FINE.

49:16.458 --> 49:17.834
OKAY, WE'RE GONNA
WORK IT OUT.

49:17.834 --> 49:19.333
I'M JUST GONNA GO
AND SEE MY DAD.

49:19.333 --> 49:21.375
- OH, NO, GOD DAMN IT.

49:21.375 --> 49:24.333
- DAD?

49:24.333 --> 49:26.166
POPS?

49:39.208 --> 49:41.584
- YOUR DEDICATION TO NICOTINE
IS ADMIRABLE.

49:41.584 --> 49:42.834
WHAT IS IT, FIVE DEGREES?

49:42.834 --> 49:46.042
- IT'S AT LEAST TEN.

49:46.042 --> 49:49.166
[lighter clicks]

49:49.166 --> 49:51.750
BIPOLAR, HUH?

49:51.750 --> 49:53.126
- CAN'T BE SURE.

49:53.126 --> 49:56.042
BUT IT LOOKED
PAINFULLY FAMILIAR.

49:56.042 --> 49:59.084
- WE SHOULD HAVE SOME OF
MONICA'S LITHIUM SOMEWHERE.

49:59.084 --> 50:02.084
IT'S NOT LIKE
SHE EVER TOOK IT.

50:04.417 --> 50:06.417
- AND I ALWAYS WORRIED
IT'D BE ME.

50:06.417 --> 50:07.959
- OH, THERE'S STILL TIME.

50:07.959 --> 50:09.250
YOU KNOW, I HEAR YOU
COULD HAVE YOUR FIRST

50:09.250 --> 50:11.042
PSYCHOTIC BREAK ANYTIME
IN YOUR TEENS OR 20s.

50:11.042 --> 50:13.168
- MENTAL ILLNESS
RUSSIAN ROULETTE

50:13.168 --> 50:15.458
WITH MONICA'S DNA
AS THE BULLET.

50:15.458 --> 50:17.041
IS ALCOHOLISM GENETIC?

50:17.041 --> 50:20.084
- IT'S THE NURTURE PART
OF NATURE AND NURTURE.

50:20.084 --> 50:21.876
ALL ABOUT THE ENVIRONMENT
YOU GROW UP IN.

50:21.876 --> 50:23.500
- OH, THAT'S VERY ENCOURAGING.

50:23.500 --> 50:25.042
JESUS.

50:25.042 --> 50:27.417
IS THIS FAMILY EVER
GONNA CATCH A BREAK?

50:27.417 --> 50:30.417
- WELL, YOU'RE
OUT OF THE POKEY,

50:30.417 --> 50:34.168
AND, UH, I PASSED
MY MIDTERMS.

50:34.168 --> 50:36.041
- THAT'S GREAT,
GOOD FOR YOU.

50:36.041 --> 50:38.041
- BARELY, BUT I PASSED.

50:38.041 --> 50:40.001
- [exhales]
I BET YOU ACED 'EM.

50:40.001 --> 50:42.542
- COLLEGE IS A LOT
FUCKING HARDER THAN IT LOOKS.

50:42.542 --> 50:45.750
YOU ACTUALLY HAVE
TO APPLY YOURSELF.

50:48.001 --> 50:49.667
- WHO EXACTLY IS AMANDA?

50:49.667 --> 50:52.041
- MY, UH, ROOMMATE'S
EX-GIRLFRIEND,

50:52.041 --> 50:53.375
WHO I ENDED UP WITH
WHEN SHE TRIED

50:53.375 --> 50:55.500
TO BLOW ME IN MY SLEEP.

50:55.500 --> 50:57.542
- SOMEBODY CAN BLOW YOU
IN YOUR SLEEP?

50:57.542 --> 50:59.125
- WELL, AT SOME POINT,
YOU WAKE UP.

50:59.125 --> 51:01.166
- [chuckles]

51:01.166 --> 51:03.041
IS IT GETTING SERIOUS?

51:03.041 --> 51:06.458
- WELL, IT'S CERTAINLY
GETTING FUCKING WEIRD.

51:06.458 --> 51:08.792
SHE BUYS ME SHIT.

51:08.792 --> 51:11.834
- NICE SHIT?
- YEAH.

51:11.834 --> 51:14.166
- SOUNDS LIKE A KEEPER.

51:22.250 --> 51:24.959
IT WAS ME, LIP.

51:24.959 --> 51:26.500
NOT FRANK.

51:26.500 --> 51:28.001
NOT MONICA.

51:28.001 --> 51:30.625
NOT NATURE.
NOT NURTURE.

51:30.625 --> 51:33.250
IT WAS ALL ME.

51:33.250 --> 51:35.917
I'M 23.

51:35.917 --> 51:38.001
IT CAN'T BE ABOUT HOW MUCH
THEY SCREWED US UP ANYMORE.

51:38.001 --> 51:39.542
- IT SOUNDS KIND OF LIKE A.A.

51:39.542 --> 51:41.126
- [chuckles]
YEAH.

51:41.126 --> 51:42.876
- YOU BEEN DRINKING
THE BIG BOOK KOOL-AID?

51:42.876 --> 51:46.208
- A BIT. ATTENDANCE IS
A CONDITION OF MY PAROLE.

51:48.750 --> 51:52.001
- YOU'RE NOT PERFECT, FIONA.

51:52.001 --> 51:54.208
NONE OF US ARE.

52:07.458 --> 52:10.375
[rock music]

52:10.375 --> 52:18.083
♪ ♪

52:19.542 --> 52:21.250
- LOOKS GOOD, GEORGE.
THANKS.

52:21.250 --> 52:23.125
HEY, CHUCKIE,
GRAB THE HOSE.

52:23.125 --> 52:26.083
HOOK UP OUR WATER, OKAY?

52:26.083 --> 52:28.584
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

52:28.584 --> 52:31.667
- HOMESTEADING.

52:31.667 --> 52:33.333
- YOU'RE CAMPING
IN MY YARD?

52:33.333 --> 52:34.667
- NOT YOUR YARD.

52:34.667 --> 52:38.000
THE VACANT LOT
NEXT TO YOUR YARD.

52:38.000 --> 52:40.000
COMPLAIN TO THE CITY
PLANNING DEPARTMENT.

52:40.000 --> 52:41.625
THEY SHOULD GET AROUND
TO SENDING SOMEBODY

52:41.625 --> 52:43.417
TO INVESTIGATE BY SUMMER.

52:43.417 --> 52:45.876
- HAVE YOU SEEN FRANK?

52:45.876 --> 52:47.917
- HE'S NOT HERE?
- NO.

52:47.917 --> 52:50.125
AND I TALKED TO DEBBIE,
AND SHE HASN'T SEEN HIM EITHER.

52:57.333 --> 53:01.126
I MADE A POT ROAST
FOR FRANK.

53:01.126 --> 53:02.917
AND IT SEEMS LIKE A SHAME
TO HAVE IT

53:02.917 --> 53:05.917
GO TO WASTE,
IF YOU GUYS ARE HUNGRY.

53:08.041 --> 53:09.917
- WE COULD EAT, THANKS.

53:09.917 --> 53:12.041
- OKAY.

53:12.041 --> 53:15.209
- CHUCKIE, POT ROAST!

53:20.542 --> 53:23.584
[melancholy music]

53:23.584 --> 53:31.625
♪ ♪

53:42.959 --> 53:45.500
- IS THIS GOOD?

53:45.500 --> 53:47.084
- GIVE ME THE BOTTLE.

53:47.084 --> 53:48.292
- ARE YOU SURE?

53:48.292 --> 53:51.292
- ABSOLUTELY.

53:58.333 --> 54:00.667
[grunts]

55:03.750 --> 55:06.584
THAT ALL YOU GOT?

55:06.584 --> 55:10.500
THAT'S IT?

55:10.500 --> 55:15.333
I'M STILL HERE, YOU FUCKER!

55:15.333 --> 55:17.208
FRANK GALLAGHER!

55:17.208 --> 55:21.667
I'M ALIVE!

55:21.667 --> 55:25.250
YOU SEE ME?

55:25.250 --> 55:29.625
YOU SEE ME STANDING HERE?

55:29.625 --> 55:33.625
[chuckle]
YOU LOST, ASSHOLE!

55:35.500 --> 55:40.125
I'M ALIVE, MOTHERFUCKER!

55:40.125 --> 55:44.876
ME, FRANK GALLAGHER!

55:44.876 --> 55:46.876
ALIVE.

55:51.125 --> 55:53.208
ALIVE.

56:06.042 --> 56:09.209
LITTLE NIP WON'T HURT YOU.

56:56.208 --> 57:01.208
[car engine]

57:01.208 --> 57:04.333
- ARE YOU GONNA GO IN?

57:06.834 --> 57:10.959
IS THIS THE RIGHT HOUSE?

57:10.959 --> 57:13.168
JACK?
- HMM?

57:13.168 --> 57:14.166
- ARE YOU GONNA GO INSIDE?

57:14.166 --> 57:19.000
- NO.
NOT TONIGHT.

57:19.000 --> 57:20.375
COME ON, LET'S GO.
